        <abstract>
            <p>Suggests that benzoic acid would be a deadly poison to bacteria and their allies.</p> 
<p>Is puzzled about the use of borax as a disinfectant because in his experiments <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> were not in the least injured by boracic acid.</p> 
        </abstract>
